# Static screenshot of `tx auth` showing 3 backends all green + cookies status
Output assets/screenshot-auth.png

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 14
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set Width 1100
Set Height 1100
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "clear && tx auth"
Enter
Sleep 5000ms
Show
Sleep 100ms
